CHANNELS
========

Usage: channels

Display all available chat channels and your subscription status.

Example output:
  === Available Channels ===
    chat [ON] - [Chat]
    ooc [ON] - [OOC]

  Use '<channel> on/off' to toggle, '<channel> history' to view history.

Each channel can be independently enabled or disabled. Your subscription
preferences are saved between sessions.

See also: chat, ooc, history
